{"tid":966691,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想溝學生妹嘅同我入一入黎","createTime":"2019-01-03T03:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T06:34:13.000Z","uid":204943,"like":27,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f15d4c1b7e0cd1bddabbd6c42f464b7381747502","tid":966691,"uid":204943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:46:25.000Z","msg":"眾所周知學生妹係最撚無知同最撚易溝<br />\n所以我呢啲老手就教教各位新手<br />\n如何有效地溝學生妹<br />\n<br />\n要去溝女就證明你唔係咩靚仔<br />\n係靚仔洗撚溝咩 啲女會出哂水咁自動送上門<br />\n所以我地教人溝女唔會教人執樣<br />\n你照住鏡自己都作嘔 點執都無柒用<br />\n<br />\n我地要靠氣勢取勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有氣勢無女溝唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以你班死毒撚做唔到好撚陽光好撚charm<br />\n就要做到毒撚的極致 有咁毒得咁毒<br />\n<br />\n少fd就要做到0fd<br />\n油頭毒撚可以試下唔剪頭髮同唔沖凉<br />\n窮撚可以試下唔食m記再食2手飯<br />\n<br />\n正所謂 柒到盡頭便是型<br />\n你會漸漸散發出一種生人勿近的氣場<br />\n咁樣你已經贏咗一半<br />\n<br />\n女人係犯賤的生物 <br />\n你愈係生人勿近 佢愈想接近<br />\n你愈係唔多理佢 佢愈想佔服你<br />\n久而久知就會有女人自動送上門<br />\n你就可以瘋狂屌女了<br />\n由死毒撚轉職成為一代傳奇fk boi <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edda22f0c0a1f98111af5c6613e0ed90bae2b41","tid":966691,"uid":107364,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10ac7a7e2a0129b97e203fc203ea82fa987086fa","tid":966691,"uid":161990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:48:52.000Z","msg":"生人勿近lv: Max"},{"pid":"37619989bbcf54b3eb04f861eb01ea9648111374","tid":966691,"uid":172507,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:50:35.000Z","